1545
01:39:38,935 --> 01:39:41,426
Were you asked to determine
the reason for these bruises?

1546
01:39:41,537 --> 01:39:45,473
- I was not.
- Where did you do the lab work?

1547
01:39:45,575 --> 01:39:47,873
St. Margaret's Hospital
in the city.

1548
01:39:47,977 --> 01:39:52,038
- Who worked up the slides for you?
