1549
01:39:52,148 --> 01:39:54,207
Wouldn't it have been better...

1550
01:39:54,317 --> 01:39:58,310
to have these slides worked up by
a pathologist or expert in this field?

1551
01:39:58,421 --> 01:40:01,413
